## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Database Configuration**:
> We propose using **Prisma ORM**. By default, we will set it up with **SQLite** so that the application can run out-of-the-box without requiring a running PostgreSQL server on your machine. Switching to **PostgreSQL** is as simple as updating the `provider = "postgresql"` in `schema.prisma` and changing the `DATABASE_URL` in the `.env` file. Please let us know if you want PostgreSQL pre-configured as the active default instead.

> [!WARNING]
> **Payment Gateway (Razorpay)**:
> Since this is a local development environment, we will build a mock Razorpay integration. It will simulate the Razorpay payment modal, verification signatures, and webhook updates. This allows testing the payment and enrollment flows seamlessly. If you have active Razorpay API keys, they can be configured in the `.env` file.

